						the product name or SKU to go to the full edit details page for that specific products.</p>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-2">
							<input type="submit" value="ADD PRODUCT" class="vend_edit_lists_buttonstyle" />
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-2 common_padding1">
							<select class="vend_edit_lists_buttonstyle" onChange="changeStatus(this);">
